<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="912000000t" end="940000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">第 5 话 软弱</p>
<p begin="947000000t" end="961000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">你没骗我们吧</p>
<p begin="965000000t" end="984000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">你们觉得我像是在开玩笑么</p>
<p begin="989000000t" end="1030000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">和久也是因为这原因么 他不是摔死的…?</p>
<p begin="1036000000t" end="1070000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">难以置信 怎么会这样</p>
<p begin="1076000000t" end="1126000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">但是和久和小高都死了…</p>
<p begin="1148000000t" end="1169000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">我也会死么…</p>
<p begin="1172000000t" end="1200000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">怎么会呢 不会死的</p>
<p begin="1203000000t" end="1215000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">会有办法的</p>
<p begin="1238000000t" end="1281000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">你说这机器人是靠生命力驱动的吧 那不去战斗不就行了</p>
<p begin="1286000000t" end="1338000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">只要不让Zearth活动 或者我们干脆不上来不就行了</p>
<p begin="1340000000t" end="1373000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">那大概不可能吧</p>
<p begin="1375000000t" end="1385000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">正是如此</p>
<p begin="1393000000t" end="1437000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">逃是可以 但是战斗开始48小时之内不能结束的话</p>
<p begin="1439000000t" end="1460000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">地球就会爆炸</p>
<p begin="1469000000t" end="1491000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">你说地球会毁灭?</p>
<p begin="1493000000t" end="1503000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">没错</p>
<p begin="1505000000t" end="1534000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">当然 如果你们输了同样会爆炸</p>
<p begin="1536000000t" end="1592000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">是为了保护地球战斗而死 还是输掉之后跟地球一起毁灭</p>
<p begin="1595000000t" end="1615000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">除此之外没有选择</p>
<p begin="1632000000t" end="1678000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">敌人可不会跟你们客气 所以还是快些消灭掉比较好</p>
<p begin="1680000000t" end="1702000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">混蛋 别开玩笑了</p>
<p begin="1721000000t" end="1742000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">别往我身上撒气啊</p>
<p begin="1747000000t" end="1796000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">你们这是用生命换来巨大的力量去保护同类</p>
<p begin="1798000000t" end="1816000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">没有比这再值得高兴的事情了吧</p>
<p begin="1823000000t" end="1859000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">要保护地球 也只能这么办了</p>
<p begin="1863000000t" end="1891000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">你说什么 谁让你表示同意了</p>
<p begin="1896000000t" end="1907000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">加古别这样</p>
<p begin="1909000000t" end="1942000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">你怎么竟然…你难道是猪吗!</p>
<p begin="1950000000t" end="1962000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">你脑袋里是猪脑子吗</p>
<p begin="1969000000t" end="2004000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">我也怕死啊</p>
<p begin="2005000000t" end="2019000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">别张嘴死闭嘴死啊死啊的</p>
<p begin="2023000000t" end="2037000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">这不是没办法吗</p>
<p begin="2052000000t" end="2081000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">因为个人应该为集体服务</p>
<p begin="2092000000t" end="2131000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">既然非这么做不可的话 就应该尽这份义务</p>
<p begin="2154000000t" end="2181000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">我也这么认为</p>
<p begin="2186000000t" end="2222000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">如果我们不去战斗 就会有很多人死去</p>
<p begin="2233000000t" end="2260000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">其中也会有我们的家人</p>
<p begin="2268000000t" end="2291000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">既然这样 就只能拼死一战了</p>
<p begin="2297000000t" end="2322000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">那你就先死给我看吧</p>
<p begin="2328000000t" end="2381000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">宇白 你就真的一点都不为可奈和家人着想吗</p>
<p begin="2381000000t" end="2419000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">别说了 宇白也有他的苦处</p>
<p begin="2433000000t" end="2466000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">他妈妈在他小时候就去世了</p>
<p begin="2469000000t" end="2476000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">宽治!</p>
<p begin="2483000000t" end="2528000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">你认为妈妈是因为可奈才死的吧</p>
<p begin="2532000000t" end="2554000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">跟你没关系 给我住嘴</p>
<p begin="2717000000t" end="2753000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">为什么我现在还要受这种罪…</p>
<p begin="2763000000t" end="2814000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">说实话 为了保护家人这理由我一点实感也没有</p>
<p begin="2822000000t" end="2847000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">更别提保护地球了</p>
<p begin="2860000000t" end="2889000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">争取有意义地度过余生吧</p>
<p begin="2909000000t" end="2932000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">请举手后提问</p>
<p begin="2937000000t" end="3005000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">首相 怪兽在这次灾难之前已经出现了两次</p>
<p begin="3011000000t" end="3030000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">政府是否清楚这个状况</p>
<p begin="3035000000t" end="3094000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">虽然已经收到相关消息 但是还不足以判断当前的状况</p>
<p begin="3103000000t" end="3146000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">在怪兽第三次出现之前 政府实际上没能采取措施吧</p>
<p begin="3152000000t" end="3191000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">出现如此严重的事件 我深表遗憾</p>
<p begin="3195000000t" end="3243000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">政府会尽最大努力支援受灾人民</p>
<p begin="3423000000t" end="3434000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">干什么</p>
<p begin="3471000000t" end="3529000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">对不起 最近你是怎么了</p>
<p begin="3531000000t" end="3563000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">如果有什么烦恼的话 不妨跟妈妈说说…</p>
<p begin="3563000000t" end="3596000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">开什么玩笑 跟你说又能怎么样</p>
<p begin="3607000000t" end="3628000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">但是你不说的话…</p>
<p begin="3642000000t" end="3662000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">我马上就要死了</p>
<p begin="3681000000t" end="3687000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">知道吗</p>
<p begin="3696000000t" end="3708000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">怎么可能知道…</p>
<p begin="3708000000t" end="3723000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">你胡说什么呢</p>
<p begin="3723000000t" end="3743000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">妈妈 算了吧</p>
<p begin="3749000000t" end="3769000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">别管他了</p>
<p begin="3808000000t" end="3824000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">你们也给我去死吧</p>
<p begin="3827000000t" end="3837000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">给我出去</p>
<p begin="3854000000t" end="3862000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">别闹了</p>
<p begin="3862000000t" end="3869000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">吵死了</p>
<p begin="3873000000t" end="3884000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">快滚</p>
<p begin="3920000000t" end="3928000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">可恶</p>
<p begin="3954000000t" end="3968000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我来了</p>
<p begin="4009000000t" end="4027000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">用不着那么害怕吧</p>
<p begin="4039000000t" end="4051000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">你来干什么</p>
<p begin="4052000000t" end="4074000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">你可真是丢人呀</p>
<p begin="4076000000t" end="4127000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">不好好表现一下的话可是没法得到本田的芳心哦</p>
<p begin="4133000000t" end="4141000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">千鹤?</p>
<p begin="4149000000t" end="4171000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">不然的话她可就被切江抢跑啦</p>
<p begin="4175000000t" end="4196000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">最近他跟千鹤可是走得很近哦</p>
<p begin="4208000000t" end="4219000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">那不可能</p>
<p begin="4236000000t" end="4264000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">她怎么可能理切江</p>
<p begin="4270000000t" end="4305000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">千鹤顶多是对我们班主任有那么点意思罢了</p>
<p begin="4315000000t" end="4330000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">没劲的家伙</p>
<p begin="4332000000t" end="4383000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">你准备怎么办 她和班主任你就放心了么</p>
<p begin="4386000000t" end="4434000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">你们的关系 你自己其实也想得很远了吧</p>
<p begin="4458000000t" end="4491000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">对了 现在就去她那里看看吧</p>
<p begin="4496000000t" end="4534000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">她现在干什么呢 说不定正在房间里换衣服</p>
<p begin="4537000000t" end="4549000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">你胡说什么</p>
<p begin="4549000000t" end="4582000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">她那么苗条 身材真不错</p>
<p begin="4596000000t" end="4635000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">反正你还是处男呢吧 就这么死了不可惜么</p>
<p begin="4641000000t" end="4667000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">不把该办的事办了可别后悔</p>
<p begin="4669000000t" end="4676000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">给我住口</p>
<p begin="4691000000t" end="4712000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">你可是快要死的人了</p>
<p begin="4799000000t" end="4821000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">你也别太宠着他了</p>
<p begin="4828000000t" end="4866000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">自己什么都干不了 却总是那么任性</p>
<p begin="4879000000t" end="4888000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">但是…</p>
<p begin="4889000000t" end="4929000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">别管他了 他在哪干些什么又跟你没关系</p>
<p begin="4931000000t" end="4941000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">可恶</p>
<p begin="4959000000t" end="4973000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">我过火了?</p>
<p begin="4977000000t" end="5017000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">怎么会 我可是去鼓励他的</p>
<p begin="5054000000t" end="5107000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">我就是喜欢看他们鼻涕眼泪又哭又闹的样子</p>
<p begin="5130000000t" end="5175000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">他倒是个有意思的家伙 跟个少爷似的</p>
<p begin="5180990000t" end="5197000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">说不定真的会输</p>
<p begin="5219000000t" end="5256000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">不过往后排也没什么意义</p>
<p begin="5447000000t" end="5468000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">不好意思 我正要出门</p>
<p begin="5475000000t" end="5501000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">你去哪 有什么事吗</p>
<p begin="5508000000t" end="5526000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">你问这些干什么</p>
<p begin="5530000000t" end="5561000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">啊 那个… 你什么时候回来呢</p>
<p begin="5564000000t" end="5578000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">我可以等你</p>
<p begin="5582000000t" end="5619000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">不知道 说不定就在外面住了</p>
<p begin="5623000000t" end="5640000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">在 在外面住?</p>
<p begin="5650000000t" end="5660000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">在哪</p>
<p begin="5672000000t" end="5711000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">喂 你要去畑饲那里吗</p>
<p begin="5749000000t" end="5768000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">你也知道了</p>
<p begin="5777000000t" end="5799000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">大家都这么传</p>
<p begin="5820000000t" end="5842000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">你们不会还在交往吧</p>
<p begin="5859000000t" end="5886000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">你傻啊 算了吧 跟那种大叔</p>
<p begin="5890000000t" end="5899000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">他不是真心的</p>
<p begin="5905000000t" end="5938000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">老师竟然跟学生交往 你不觉得奇怪吗</p>
<p begin="5998000000t" end="6015000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">那是我跟老师两个人的事</p>
<p begin="6177000000t" end="6196000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">老师不在么</p>
<p begin="6213000000t" end="6232000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">没有来电</p>
<p begin="6263000000t" end="6280000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">怎么 不在家吗</p>
<p begin="6285000000t" end="6313000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">是故意躲着你吧</p>
<p begin="6427000000t" end="6467000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">千鹤 有时间的话 去趟铃森水族馆吧</p>
<p begin="6491000000t" end="6519000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">那有海豚 你喜欢海豚吧</p>
<p begin="6524000000t" end="6546000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">听说铃森那特别好</p>
<p begin="6561000000t" end="6585000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">跟其他水族馆不一样的</p>
<p begin="6589000000t" end="6594000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">走吧</p>
<p begin="6594000000t" end="6609000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">现在就去</p>
<p begin="6635000000t" end="6657000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">你只是想跟我上床吧</p>
<p begin="6689000000t" end="6730000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">告诉我 我和老师之间的事传出来多少了</p>
<p begin="6734000000t" end="6769000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">大家都知道么 我跟老师上过床的事</p>
<p begin="6792000000t" end="6799000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">上过了?</p>
<p begin="6808000000t" end="6874000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">被老师抱的时候 不只是身体 连心都得到了满足</p>
<p begin="6931000000t" end="6943000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">开什么玩笑</p>
<p begin="6969000000t" end="7009000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">别…别说了 你不知道你只是被玩弄吗</p>
<p begin="7215000000t" end="7251000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">我是国防部军司令部的森本</p>
<p begin="7256000000t" end="7268000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">国防部?</p>
<p begin="7274000000t" end="7317000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">关于那个黑色的怪兽 有些事情需要问你</p>
<p begin="7542000000t" end="7563000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">要把我们带到哪去</p>
<p begin="7569000000t" end="7615000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">不知道 好像是古茂田跟他爸爸说了</p>
<p begin="7621000000t" end="7632000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">所以才会这样?</p>
<p begin="7636000000t" end="7643000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">不知道</p>
<p begin="7713000000t" end="7724000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">好小的军舰</p>
<p begin="7725000000t" end="7775000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">开什么玩笑 这可是妙高型重巡洋舰 全日本最强的啊</p>
<p begin="7789000000t" end="7806000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">加古呢</p>
<p begin="7806000000t" end="7827000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">真的 没看到他</p>
<p begin="7834000000t" end="7855000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">我们现在正在找加古功</p>
<p begin="7866000000t" end="7893000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">只要找到他 也会让他来的</p>
<p begin="7903000000t" end="7918000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">里面请</p>
<p begin="7945000000t" end="7962000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">不好意思 突然把你们请来</p>
<p begin="7978000000t" end="8027000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">恐怕你们也很吃惊 不过这事情确实不好解释</p>
<p begin="8035000000t" end="8052000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">现在也还没有通知你们的家长</p>
<p begin="8055000000t" end="8106000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">你们认识我们? 知道我们所做的事?</p>
<p begin="8121000000t" end="8155000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">我们也并不是袖手旁观</p>
<p begin="8162000000t" end="8194000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">只是没有准确情报的话 是不能行动的</p>
<p begin="8227000000t" end="8292000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">但是内阁官房调查室总指挥要求将你们作为甲类特别人士进行保护</p>
<p begin="8296000000t" end="8303000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">保护?</p>
<p begin="8309000000t" end="8361000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">以后 我们将为你们提供24小时贴身保卫</p>
<p begin="8364000000t" end="8380000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">是为了保护我们吗</p>
<p begin="8384000000t" end="8409000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">但是 万一被召唤到Zearth里面去的话…</p>
<p begin="8413000000t" end="8423000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">Zearth?</p>
<p begin="8430000000t" end="8512000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">Zearth是我们起的名字 如果被它所召唤 我们就必须去战斗</p>
<p begin="8517000000t" end="8541000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">目前已有上万人死亡</p>
<p begin="8549000000t" end="8609000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">如果坐视不管 日本乃至全世界都会有更多人受害</p>
<p begin="8614000000t" end="8646000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">我们不能让你们负这个责任</p>
<p begin="8653000000t" end="8678000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">我们会安全吗</p>
<p begin="8683000000t" end="8724000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">现在这个问题是国家最优先解决的事情</p>
<p begin="8729000000t" end="8753000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我们也已经开始着手调查</p>
<p begin="8756000000t" end="8778000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">希望你们能协助我们</p>
<p begin="8806000000t" end="8825000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">那么 我来介绍一下</p>
<p begin="8829000000t" end="8849000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">关政光 一等海尉</p>
<p begin="8854000000t" end="8875000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">田中美纯 一等空尉</p>
<p begin="8989000000t" end="9015000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">我们想要调查这个</p>
<p begin="9021000000t" end="9054000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">突然出现在日本的未知物体</p>
<p begin="9070000000t" end="9108000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">被你们叫做Zearth的它 现在在哪</p>
<p begin="9111000000t" end="9120000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">不知道</p>
<p begin="9122000000t" end="9149000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">会不会在海里</p>
<p begin="9161000000t" end="9227000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">它并不由我们管理 我们只不过是棋子而已</p>
<p begin="9238000000t" end="9244000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">大概…</p>
<p begin="9249000000t" end="9291000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">那么 如果我们想去 该怎么办呢</p>
<p begin="9295000000t" end="9313000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">你们是怎么去的</p>
<p begin="9315000000t" end="9330000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">得靠肥虫 对吧</p>
<p begin="9342000000t" end="9350000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">那是什么</p>
<p begin="9351000000t" end="9405000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">怎么说呢 直接见面会比较容易理解</p>
<p begin="9414000000t" end="9422000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">能见到吗</p>
<p begin="9429000000t" end="9444000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">如果叫它的话 大概能…</p>
<p begin="9452000000t" end="9464000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">肥虫</p>
<p begin="9466000000t" end="9494000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">肥虫</p>
<p begin="9494000000t" end="9527000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">肥虫</p>
<p begin="9582000000t" end="9593000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">肥虫</p>
<p begin="9609000000t" end="9625000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">来了 你们叫我吗</p>
<p begin="9639000000t" end="9678000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">被这么可爱的孩子们呼唤 我只好出来了</p>
<p begin="9704000000t" end="9719000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">你就是肥虫同学吗</p>
<p begin="9721000000t" end="9735000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">别叫“同学”</p>
<p begin="9738000000t" end="9753000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">那叫 肥虫…</p>
<p begin="9764000000t" end="9812000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">叫我肥虫大人 亏你还是个成年人 怎么这么不懂事</p>
<p begin="9860000000t" end="9880000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">那么 怎么样</p>
<p begin="9884000000t" end="9917000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">我们希望去调查Zearth…</p>
<p begin="9935000000t" end="9953000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">你们是白痴吗</p>
<p begin="9957000000t" end="9985000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">那可不是你们能明白的东西</p>
<p begin="9990000000t" end="10020000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">就像猴子想要弄懂神的东西一样</p>
<p begin="10023000000t" end="10036000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">我也这么想</p>
<p begin="10038000000t" end="10067000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">但是实际上 这个国家正在遭受灾难</p>
<p begin="10072000000t" end="10130000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">希望您能理解 我们想要查清这场灾难的迫切心情</p>
<p begin="10151000000t" end="10160000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">真会说话</p>
<p begin="10169000000t" end="10212000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">但是他们可不是为了什么国家这种小地方而战的</p>
<p begin="10221000000t" end="10238000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">是为了这个星球</p>
<p begin="10253000000t" end="10275000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">没功夫凑你们的热闹</p>
<p begin="10303990000t" end="10313990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">带我们去</p>
<p begin="10330000000t" end="10358000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">无可救药就是说你这种人</p>
<p begin="10363990000t" end="10392000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">也不搞清对方的实力就动手</p>
<p begin="10398990000t" end="10410000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">想去就让你去</p>
<p begin="10496000000t" end="10506000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">快带他去医务室</p>
<p begin="10506000000t" end="10511000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">是</p>
<p begin="10519000000t" end="10529000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">把手也拿上</p>
<p begin="10533000000t" end="10550000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">肥虫 太过分了</p>
<p begin="10552000000t" end="10563000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">为什么这样</p>
<p begin="10577000000t" end="10601000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">敢向我提意见?</p>
<p begin="10634000000t" end="10678000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">好了好了 别跟他计较 肥虫先生</p>
<p begin="10688000000t" end="10726000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">“先生”啊…还不赖</p>
<p begin="10731000000t" end="10768000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">既然我们这群孩子代表这颗星球登上了Zearth</p>
<p begin="10773000000t" end="10810000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">不如也让我们代表这颗星球前往调查</p>
<p begin="10810000000t" end="10847000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">你们也被选上了? 别开玩笑了</p>
<p begin="10850000000t" end="10898000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">我明白了 那么肥虫先生 我们放弃调查</p>
<p begin="10903000000t" end="10912000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">喂 你…</p>
<p begin="10916000000t" end="10945000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">毕竟我们只是在征得同意</p>
<p begin="10947000000t" end="10985000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">你倒不像那帮白痴 挺懂事的嘛</p>
<p begin="10990000000t" end="11019000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">作为条件 请允许我去参观</p>
<p begin="11068000000t" end="11105000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">我喜欢你 就让你调查吧</p>
<p begin="11113000000t" end="11146000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">顺便让你体会一下自己是多么的弱小</p>
<p begin="11253000000t" end="11262000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">结果如何</p>
<p begin="11271000000t" end="11278000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">是</p>
<p begin="11295000000t" end="11315000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">样本采集失败了</p>
<p begin="11324000000t" end="11334000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">无法切削么</p>
<p begin="11334000000t" end="11340000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">是的</p>
<p begin="11365000000t" end="11382000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">光学数据可靠吗</p>
<p begin="11388000000t" end="11440000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">各种波长的光被不规则地反射 并不稳定</p>
<p begin="11445000000t" end="11465000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">这还真是麻烦啊</p>
<p begin="11466000000t" end="11472000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">是的</p>
<p begin="11477000000t" end="11502000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">可能雷达也无法捕捉到它</p>
<p begin="11514000000t" end="11523000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">从外观上看</p>
<p begin="11525000000t" end="11588000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">除了外骨骼构造 以及可能是用作装甲的板状物之外</p>
<p begin="11591000000t" end="11602000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">其他一无所知</p>
<p begin="11622000000t" end="11652000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">仔细看看…总有种奇怪的感觉</p>
<p begin="11661000000t" end="11716000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">这种无法接近…被拒之千里的空虚感 难道是我的错觉么</p>
<p begin="11716000000t" end="11754000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">不 队员门也都这么说</p>
<p begin="11782000000t" end="11802000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">笹見 笹見</p>
<p begin="11811000000t" end="11830000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">不行 无线电不通</p>
<p begin="11841000000t" end="11854000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">真是令人不可思议的地方啊</p>
<p begin="11864000000t" end="11886000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">到底是靠什么的力量呢</p>
<p begin="11901000000t" end="11927000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">这是什么? 你们的椅子?</p>
<p begin="11934000000t" end="11940000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">是</p>
<p begin="11945000000t" end="11965000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">战斗的时候就坐在上面</p>
<p begin="11969000000t" end="12026000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">这些椅子跟家里面的椅子是相通的 可以在两地间移动</p>
<p begin="12029000000t" end="12046000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">只有你们可以?</p>
<p begin="12051000000t" end="12062000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">大概是…</p>
<p begin="12067000000t" end="12082000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">围成了一个圈…</p>
<p begin="12087000000t" end="12118000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">战斗的时候周围会显示出外面的样子</p>
<p begin="12209000000t" end="12237000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">怎…怎么办 又来了…</p>
<p begin="12241000000t" end="12249000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">不要…</p>
<p begin="12259000000t" end="12267000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">不要!</p>
<p begin="12271000000t" end="12289000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">怎么了 冷静下来</p>
<p begin="12432000000t" end="12441000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">听到了吗</p>
<p begin="12452000000t" end="12456000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">没有</p>
<p begin="12464000000t" end="12470000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">是谁</p>
<p begin="12483000000t" end="12505000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">说吧 是谁的椅子</p>
<p begin="12513000000t" end="12523000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">是加古的</p>
<p begin="12532000000t" end="12563000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">啊呀 忘记叫上加古了</p>
<p begin="12581000000t" end="12600000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">是加古的…</p>
<p begin="12608000000t" end="12623000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">好可怜</p>
<p begin="12788000000t" end="12795000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">真的假的</p>
<p begin="12801000000t" end="12823000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">为什么是我</p>
<p begin="12837000000t" end="12846000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">这不是真的!</p>
<p begin="13846000000t" end="13858000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">为什么是我</p>
<p begin="13863000000t" end="13890000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">为什么我这么倒霉</p>
<p begin="13894000000t" end="13902000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">我不想死</p>
<p begin="13908000000t" end="13920000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">救救我</p>
